company_name: LEO RABEL, OBST- UND GEMUSEGROS- HANDELSGESELLSCHAFT M.B.H.
information: The company LEO RABEL, OBST- UND GEMUSEGROS- HANDELSGESELLSCHAFT M.B.H., is a Wholesaler, founded in 1965, which operates in the Fruits and vegetables - import-export industry. It is based in Ottendorf An Der Rittschein, Austria.
